<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3269132>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18–26. Stictotettix cleyerae sp. nov. Male abdominal sternal apodemes (18), ♀ 7th abdominal sternite (19) and ♂ genitalia (20–26).—20, Genital capsule in lateral view; 21, pygofer in dorsal view; 22, subgenital plate in ventral view; 23, style and connective in dorsal view; 24, aedeagus in lateral view; 25, 26, aedeagal apex in caudal (25) and dorsal (26) views. Scales: 0.05 mm (25, 26), 0.1 mm (23, 24), 0.2 mm (18–22)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3269132/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

